Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:30.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:37.31,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:44.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:51.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:01:00.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:05.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:10.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:16.48,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:22.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抵达南极秘密基地的 强与娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长将鲸鱼伊里恩 介绍给他们认识
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伊里恩预言娜蒂亚会再见到 她的爸爸与哥哥后便离去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了寻找新亚特兰提斯的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号今天也仍航行于大海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:50.47,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#20 强的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 首先是流通经济方面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至上个月为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由于长嘴硬鳞鱼号l型 所进行的通商破坏计划
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,羊毛等输出输入品 有80%皆已落入我方手中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前对各国的武器输出 也顺利进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,利润较原定高出3%
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新亚特兰提斯目前掌控了 全世界80分之1的货币
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再来是军事方面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空中战舰二号舰 已经组装60%
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该可按照原定日期完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,此外 组装完成的 七艘长嘴硬鳞鱼号ll型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可于近期正式服役
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今日已开始着手建造 巴别塔第2号炉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号的情况呢？\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自从A号作战之后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尚未能确认其生存与否
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是沉没了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沉没现场并未发现 鹦鹉螺号的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对方可是尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定正躲在某处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暗中查探我们的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 我是艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,副船长 抱歉打扰你休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请到舰桥来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在距离三万处 发现疑似长嘴硬鳞鱼号的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了 立刻过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有低血压的毛病真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上起床真累
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早\N安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你认为呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也无法判断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是故障吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许是鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 先以定向电波进行确认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来扮鬼脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这阵子不是窝在 艾丽朵拉那里看书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是在制作新发明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都不过来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚也跟我们一起玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为强都不来找你玩 所以你觉得无聊对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是那样呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 对不起喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吗？好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我们去找强玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好不好？玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这招假哭是谁教你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是桑森教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说为了生存 就需要某些非常手段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些人净会教些有的没的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌 现在明明不是感冒的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 竟然有幸 帮心爱的尼莫先生洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真是世界上最有福报的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:06:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好歹也为 被迫作陪的人想一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然要我桑森大爷洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说那什么话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今后的时代潮流就是 不会做家事的男人就没有女人爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 海上男儿的 尼莫船长则另当别论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 还顺利吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,顺利极了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就快完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,作工精细 期待它大功告成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个就是那个吗？ 可以在空中飞的机器吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是这次的却没有螺旋桨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个发明是藉由燃烧空气与燃料 再朝后方喷出火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,利用其反动力来飞上天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个自动开关阀是它的特征喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 现在输出功率很弱 还没办法载人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会又是个耍人的发明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题 理论非常完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你等着 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定会用这个发明 带你去非洲的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完成了吗？\N完成了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 要开始实验了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成了 成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 真的飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的理论是很完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒\N好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是攻击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才那是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是强的发明失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 让人虚惊一场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反应又出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个家伙… 果然是长嘴硬鳞鱼号吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因为刚才的爆炸声 泄漏了位置吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着那么沮丧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对对对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经历愈多失败 男人才会愈来愈坚强啊 强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题 用不着担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我早就猜到会发生这样的事 所以偷偷的另外做了一架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是因为你想着 还有第二次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以第一次才掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才会造成这样的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真受不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,急速潜航 急速潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,位于上甲板人员 立刻返回舰内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危机出现\N大事不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头 快走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好不容易才把衣服重新洗好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么还在说这些！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,留得青山在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫先生的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不要走 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深度50公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,速度3分之1
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离长嘴硬鳞鱼号还有1万2千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,确实朝我方前进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被对方发现了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主动声纳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尚未发出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要主动出击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 对方应该并不晓得 我们还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认为应该趁这个机会 一口气展开攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我们连长嘴硬鳞鱼号 在哪里都不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种靠运气的作战未免…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敌我的兵力差已经高达20比1
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们还有其它的作战方法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,定向主动声纳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能被对方发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰就战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？发现鹦鹉螺号了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第28号传来以下讯息 『遭遇鹦鹉螺号 准备开战』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 尼莫还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用理会 继续报告\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根据自爆的巴别塔第1号炉资料 重新检讨的结果如下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与第28号的通讯刚才中断
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,判断已遭击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又是尼莫的鹦鹉螺号？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到那根眼中钉又跑了回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 既然鹦鹉螺号还在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘空中战舰就有了 测试性能的最佳材料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,游戏也该告个段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.88,0:12:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们可不是在玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是这种回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你晓得自己做错了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使是个小失误
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有时也会攸关 许多人的性命安危
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,千万别忘了这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强被尼莫骂过之后 他在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又开始制作飞机了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他不气馁 又开始制作起飞机了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这小孩既肯努力又有毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.23,0:12:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小孩是桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家一起吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是堂堂的绅士桑森耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沦落到这种地步 真的好悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,辛苦维持至今的形象全都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森 也该换人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先等我将液状硬化玻陨石完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强的发明 燃起你的竞争斗志了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么不去找艾丽朵拉陪你玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不要呢 那个阿姨好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老是要人家念书 好讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听到了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听起来像是个要求教养 很能干的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在强那边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真羡慕那对青春期情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只会一直回答是是是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你又不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却不敢反驳半句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真是没用！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:14:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法啊 毕竟错的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 那么快就认输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的 因为我还是个小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,头发好碍事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去帮你向尼莫船长抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么事吗？娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是在船长室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长室？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长 娜蒂亚说想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了 我这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么要责备强？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还不懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:14:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 我是不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么强得被骂得那么惨？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟现在的你解释也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好狡猾 你想逃避是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你先冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算被长嘴硬鳞鱼号发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正最后还是会打赢对方 有什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种事不是小孩子能插嘴的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大人总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要情势对自己不利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就会用小孩子作借口 不把人当成一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我最讨厌大人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别说出那么伤人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你就垂头丧气地逃回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也有过这样的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总觉得大人做的事都好肮脏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也有过青春期吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么话 真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不过才20多岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然当时我无法接受 大人的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但后来我明白 凡事都是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大人所做的事都是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总有一天 你也会怀念起 自己的青春岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话说回来 你的男朋友强 跑哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这么要紧的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想他应该又去找艾丽朵拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要小心别被艾丽朵拉 把强给抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.46,0:16:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强的母亲很早就过世了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他要不是有恋母情结 就是有恋姐情结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不晓得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是会憧憬年长女性的男生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只女狐狸太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不光是尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就连小孩子都不放过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪 有人在谈论我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是有人正在称赞 你是个美人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 真会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这种话要对娜蒂亚说才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟娜蒂亚说行不通的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算跟她说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她也只会认为我在撒谎 根本就不肯相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有女孩被赞美会不开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做什么…我是来请教她 乙太理论不懂的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,骗人 你那个头是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还让她帮你剪了头发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一找到理由 就老爱往艾丽朵拉的房里钻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…你误会了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可就难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你今天好漂亮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常漂亮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是怎么了？强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发烧了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我听说没有女孩 被赞美会不开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是谁告诉你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我最讨厌你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强老是跟艾丽朵拉混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢迎光临 真是稀客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？ 强有跟你说了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,关于那件事 我想跟你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我们一起去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你觉得强这个人怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛 他就像弟弟一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请你别再对强灌输一些 奇怪的观念了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你觉得强怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你觉得尼莫船长怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:19:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛 我喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你很意外吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种冷酷的男人哪里好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷酷的男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 他也因此而受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.01,0:20:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他杀过许多人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 总有一天 他一定会负起责任的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.71,0:20:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不是有他在 我也没办法活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自从13年前那时起 他不知道救过我多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明这么危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么还要坚持与石像鬼 以及新亚特兰提斯对抗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必须有人来阻止 他们暴虐无道的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前做得到这件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只有与他们拥有 同等科学力量的鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还真是说得冠冕堂皇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冠冕堂皇？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人在进行某种行为时 所必须要有的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 不光是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,报仇？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 我曾经有个弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾经？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那他现在人在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这13年来他都跟我的父母 待在同一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,13年前 有个男人毁灭了我的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们就是那个时候遇害的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是石像鬼做的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 好过份的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个时候 是尼莫船长救了你的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有其他的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后来那些人聚集了起来 建造了这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了向石像鬼以及他的组织 新亚特兰提斯报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好洗干净喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:21:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,指甲也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你打算让那些孩子 在船上待到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.52,0:22:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新亚特兰提斯 的确想抓娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她待在这里或许比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但没人晓得这艘船 何时会沉没
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难不成你打算 与娜蒂亚同生死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,确认接近中的航行物 为长嘴硬鳞鱼号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.81,0:22:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 请立刻至舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.21,0:22:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了 我马上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.21,0:22:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就战斗位置 副船长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真吓人 第6艘出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,四面八方都被团团包围住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这片海域水深不到300
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:22:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,船长 10点钟方向有克马得海沟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两舷全速 朝克马得海沟前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如同计划 鹦鹉螺号转进克马得海沟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鳖要进瓮了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很快就要跟你永别了 尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰就第一种战斗位置\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰就第一种战斗位置
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.60,0:23:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备对潜水艇战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非战斗员退避至第三区
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回的情况似乎不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.74,0:23:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,气氛相当紧绷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.01,0:23:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在寻找鹦鹉螺号的声纳声 也比平常多出许多
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.70,0:24:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回是真的打算击沉这艘船吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.18,0:24:19.38,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.45,0:24:27.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.56,0:24:32.66,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.73,0:24:36.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.03,0:24:45.94,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.01,0:24:56.01,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.09,0:25:04.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.90,0:25:09.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.20,0:25:13.76,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.84,0:25:23.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.22,0:25:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受到石像鬼的海空夹击
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.76,0:25:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号面临存亡危机
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.80,0:25:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这个紧要关头
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.06,0:25:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝、桑森、韩森三人组
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.60,0:25:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然驾着葛兰坦先跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.84,0:25:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼 我愿意把蔚蓝之水交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.64,0:25:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要再互相残杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.24,0:25:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『再见了…鹦鹉螺号』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.91,0:25:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔\N要看喔
